  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7581317/" class="title-link">还成吧</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7581317"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1762183/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1762183/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">北风扬雪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-08-26"
      class="main-meta">2015-08-26 14:55:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7581317_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  周老师这个作品是毕业论文改的，可惜附件没加上略感遗憾。 对老红军GWS的采访有点意思，现在敢调查这个的人不多，G老爷子胆子也不小。 另外书中也是有错误的，比如把人名搞错了，写日记的不是吴玉章，是谢觉哉。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7581317_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7581317_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
